6. Security & Compliance
Key Security: API keys are hashed in the database; no plain text storage.
Encryption: Strict HTTPS/TLS enforcement for all PII transit.
Privacy: Search queries are stored in encrypted audit logs and never used for AI training (GDPR/NDPR compliant).

7. GTM (Go To Market) Strategy
The Hook: "The Unified Compliance API for Global and Pan-African Fintechs. Stop building OFAC parsers and scraping CBN PDFs."
Documentation First: Marketing centered on beautiful, functional API documentation (ReadMe/Swagger).
Targeting: CTOs and Compliance Heads at Seed/Series A Fintechs across Africa (e.g., Paystack, Moniepoint) and global firms expanding into the continent.

